      <title>台湾监管机构拒绝中国信托银行以 41 亿美元收购新光银行的提议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/taiwan-regulator-rejects-ctbc-s-4-1-billion-bid-for-shin-kong</link>
