      <title>交易员认为美联储降息半个百分点的可能性大于降息四分之一个百分点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/dollar-slides-near-lowest-since-january-on-large-fed-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券交易员再次认为，美联储决策者在本周会议上将利率下调半个百分点而非四分之一个百分点的可能性更大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/dollar-slides-near-lowest-since-january-on-large-fed-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 04:26:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场等待美联储降息的关键一周伊始，比特币价格出现下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/bitcoin-btc-slips-as-edgy-global-markets-await-fed-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在市场普遍预期美联储将降息之际，比特币出现回落，本周晚些时候美联储将公布这一政策变化，全球市场对此感到紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/bitcoin-btc-slips-as-edgy-global-markets-await-fed-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 02:42:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
